{"tid":1495851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"監控燈柱關注組稱有成員往中國時一度被扣約20小時","createTime":"2019-08-22T08:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T09:00:02.000Z","uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2b1a27accd73591681aa38d921e8af06f0f8d9","tid":1495851,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"監控燈柱關注組成員、化名史先生，出席民間記者會時表示，關注組有一名40幾歲男成員，於剛過去的周末，經福田口岸前往內地期間，被扣留約20小時。<br />\n<br />\n史先生稱，該名成員被公安問話，期間公安曾經檢查他的手機，並拿出一張相信是該名成員參與和平示威期間的相片，亦曾致電該名成員的親友，詢問成員的基本資料，該名成員最後被收集指模，及簽署悔改書後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方就元朗721襲擊事件控告兩名男子參與暴動，民間記者會發言人、化名黃先生表示，在事發一個月後才作出檢控是太遲，質疑警方拖延調查工作，保障不到市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476124-20190822.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476124-20190822.htm&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=3b9d0637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476124-20190822.htm&h=18782cb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476124-20190822.htm</a>"},{"pid":"173be963469a4ad49bdb5f802e427e74f1465be9","tid":1495851,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5839dd64f68695b7cdb8b103f34428469d3a2e77","tid":1495851,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978ca6a14dc68ddc4c38c6ecb8692902765affff","tid":1495851,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201